AIM:
To generate the Hash code using HashCalc Tool.  

PROCEDURE :
Step 1: Download the HashCalc tool from https://hashcalc.en.softonic.com/ 
Step 2: Install it and Open tool. 
Step 3: Now choose any type of File to calculate the different Cryptographic hash for it. 
Step 4: Choose three dots on Data: Column and select any type of file from the system.
 

Step 5: Now click on Calculate, and the Default marked hashes will be calculated on display.  

 

Step 6: We can mark other than Default settings on it. Try with other cryptographical has that were unmarked on default
